title: 'We didn't get it right' - Key apologises for Ashes performance
subtitle: Director of England cricket Rob Key says he is "gutted, disappointed and sorry" for England's dismal performance in the Ashes series, having lost the series with two matches still to play.
full_text: Director of England cricket Rob Key says he is "gutted, disappointed and sorry" for England's dismal performance in the Ashes series, having lost the series with two matches still to play.
